{"tid":804743,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺d人娶老婆要人俾人情好小家？","createTime":"2018-09-03T08:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T09:33:40.000Z","uid":60491,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"236825cea1ebec3158c901d98587434443e335db","tid":804743,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"講到娶老婆係一件好開心嘅事<br />\n但係又要周圍死r爛r 「小弟結婚，有無時間出席嚟飲？」<br />\n難聽d講 根本就係「我結婚，幫幫手籌下旗」<br />\n<br />\n既然你娶老婆咁高興 又講到大喜日子 咁做乜要人俾錢 請人食飯算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫人俾錢去食你d爛鬼餸菜同睇你地懶係恩愛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得擺酒同做show無分別，結婚姐，叫晒最好嘅朋友一齊食餐飯咪得，你結婚洗錢係你嘅事，做乜要人去食飯俾人情補貼你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：個d幾年唔搵一次嘅「朋友」問我去唔去飲 有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84eccd40850aaaa5936e279d20eee91cfa1ca3a8","tid":804743,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"我又娶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e928d516c3532fb543c7a91649e1766c8f8e8388","tid":804743,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84eccd40850aaaa5936e279d20eee91cfa1ca3a8","tid":804743,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"我又娶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:08:52.000Z","msg":"已經九月了，生日都過埋"},{"pid":"05a9824a6e7ee8f9df373b73aa33960535f4d3ac","tid":804743,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e928d516c3532fb543c7a91649e1766c8f8e8388","tid":804743,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84eccd40850aaaa5936e279d20eee91cfa1ca3a8","tid":804743,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c